getIdentity(address).details: Retrieves the identity details for a given owner address.

params._owner: The address of the identity owner.

returns.isRegistered_: True if the identity is registered, false otherwise.
returns.name: The name of the identity owner.

params._name: The name associated with the identity.

updateIdentity(string,string).details: Updates the digital identity for the caller (msg.sender).
